            <h5 class="column-head" data-uuid="5650109771b74f7abd0548563a7ea76d">Union Membership, 1880–1900</h5>
            <p class="intro" data-uuid="5016826f64e049798d4cbad31d030883">Major events like the Haymarket Riot (1886) and the Pullman strike (1894) affected workers’ willingness to unionize.  </p>
